ActCanadian Multiculturalism Act
SubjectOrder Designating the Minister of Canadian Heritage as the Minister for the Purposes of the Canadian Multiculturalism Act
PrecisOrder (1) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2023-771 of July 26, 2023; and (2) designating the Minister of CANADIAN HERITAGE, a member of the King's Privy Council for Canada, as the MINISTER for the purposes of the CANADIAN MULTICULTURALISM ACT.
